						</a>
						<a href="https://swbsnewby7.tistory.com" target="_blank" class="contact-card">
							<Icon icon="pencil-line" size="2.5rem" />
							<p>Blog</p>
						</a>
						<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dongwook7/" target="_blank" class="contact-card">
							<Icon icon="linkedin-logo" size="2.5rem" />
